items.checkin_comment:
Carwyn Canvent 2025 #22:
Sour cherries, overripe peach, lovely, lingering acidity on top a dry finish. Slightly tame for what I’d expect of a Flanders style ale, though that probably makes it a bit more approachable for many! A great brew.
